{"title":"Revel Bikes is Having a Huge Warehouse Sale","link":"https://theradavist.com/revel-bikes-warehouse-sale/","date":1706564706000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/04/Revel-Rover-Review-1.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>As the bike industry continues to contract after a multi-year expansion riding the post-COVID boom, brands we work with continue to have sales. Now’s the time to take advantage! Revel just announced a massive warehouse sale as they move into a new shipping warehouse and included in the list of bikes marked down are the <a href=\"https://revelbikes.com/shop-in-stock/?_model=rover\" target=\"_blank\">Rover gravel bikes</a> and the Big Iron titanium fat bike in size <a href=\"https://revelbikes.com/product/big-iron-sram-gx-eagle/?attribute_pa_frame-size=medium\" target=\"_blank\">medium</a> and <a href=\"https://revelbikes.com/product/big-iron-sram-gx-eagle/?attribute_pa_frame-size=large\" target=\"_blank\">large</a>.</p>\n<p>Check out the full warehouse sale at Revel and see our coverage of some of Revel’s bikes below in the related archives…</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/revel-bikes-warehouse-sale/\">Revel Bikes is Having a Huge Warehouse Sale</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"c4a101295edcb4b3f2019aadf3ef03e435eecad265b3a161a0508292d7f599c6","category":"Cycling"}